            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "This school is the best!! I am a 7th standard student right now and I am studying in this school for 8 years i. e. Class prep to class 7th. The teachers are amazing and always give their best in making us clear the concept. We also have co-curricular activities of our choice and we go to many excursions. In parents teachers meeting,  the teacher give honest feedback about us to our parents. The school organizes many activities like model united nations, inter-class and inter-school competitions,  Olympian, asset exam and many more.\n\nI just want to say that I love this school and I will also perform better in academics and sports.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
