          "reviewBody": "Every school has two phase, same some teacher are good and some not. I think it's teacher responsibility to take care the overall growth of children, but some teacher are not up to that level , I don't want to take name in this plateform.\nSchool have to organize teachers FDP about how to handle Childern with care and love.\nSome teachers shouts in class and and children not able to tell them their problems.\nSchool have to take care this and can also take the feedback form children also about their teachers.\nDon't make school only money making maching.",
